ted by more massive dark matter halos with\na simple one-to-one correspondence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jun 2003 18:05:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Aug 2003 13:52:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
